[4]
Date: Thu, 4 Sep 1997 13:04:03 -0600
From: Kevin Johnson <kevin@johnsonk.opa.hd.co.harris.tx.us>
In my previous report I had inadvertently included prions in the list of
pathogens killed. Prions should not have been included. Irradiation does
not affect proteins but [does affect] DNA and RNA.
Please forgive my error.
---
Kevin Johnson
